Rushing for the exit, Blackfang jumps and braces to the ceiling as the 
plasma shots come at him. He drops back down and continues running, 
giving Kup no answer.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., RoboRick007 <rfa007@c...> wrote:
> : : Kup / Rodimus Prime : :
> 
> Kup is surprised and goes down. He drops his rifle.
> 
> Kup: What the hell Blackfang, why are you doing this?
> 
> Rodimus hears banging from behind him and rushes into the room 
again. He fires two plasma shots at Blackfang.
> 
> Meanwhile Kup tries to kick Blackfang off.
